{"id":193047,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/11/你使用了多少个密码？/","date":"2011-11-01T09:01:07Z","modified":"2011-11-01T09:01:07Z","title":"你使用了多少个密码？","content":"<p>《大西洋月刊》记者James Fallows讲述了他妻子的亲身经历：Gmail帐号被黑客控制和删除，数年电子邮件通信全数消失。在联系了Gmail团队之后，只有今年的上千封邮件恢复，对于以前的邮件Google表示了“遗憾”。他与Google进行了多次交涉，邮件终于全部恢复，随后他立即通过Thunderbird将邮件备份到硬盘和其它地方。在采访了Google雇员后，他了解到每天有数千邮箱被短暂劫持用于发送垃圾邮件。他询问专业人士有多少密码，他们的回答是多至一打少至四个，大部分人有五到六个，并且分门别类的管理好密码。Google的Michael Jones说，业内人士始终考虑着风险，而普通人只有在品尝到失败的滋味后才会铭记于心。<img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/19b2ab7d/mf.gif\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E4%BD%A0%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%86%E5%A4%9A%E5%B0%91%E4%B8%AA%E5%AF%86%E7%A0%81%EF%BC%9F&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F10%2F31%2F1031250%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/11/260f6417emailthis2.gif.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E4%BD%A0%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%86%E5%A4%9A%E5%B0%91%E4%B8%AA%E5%AF%86%E7%A0%81%EF%BC%9F&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F10%2F31%2F1031250%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/11/044291a1bookmark.gif.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/117330722265/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/19b2ab7d/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/117330722265/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/19b2ab7d/a2.img\" border=\"0\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=-2x_25kxrhw:CMWsJVWwGrU:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=-2x_25kxrhw:CMWsJVWwGrU:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.f